			</label>
			<label>
			  <text>&lt;html&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To use the "Bell" setting and the rotate bell function (default on F9, when the bell is ringing):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text>
			</label>
			<label>
			  <text>For each function to have the bell assigned to it, select only the first choice, as listed above</text>
			</label>
			<label>
			  <text>Note: With this config only one bell can be configured at a time</text>
			</label>
			<label>
			  <text>   </text>
			</label>
			<label>
			  <text>&lt;html&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To have different bells on different functions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text>
			</label>
			<label>
			  <text>Set "Bell" to first choice as listed above</text>
			</label>
			<label>
			  <text>For each function, select the desired bell name from the bell group</text>
			</label>
			<label>
			  <text>Do not use the rotate whistle/horn function while bell is ringing, to prevent accidental changes, remap F9 to something else and do not have rotate whistle/horn mapped to anything</text>
			</label>
		</group>
